WEBVTT

00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:03.000
Welcome to Sub Loader!

00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:06.000
This is a test subtitle file

00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:09.000
Try loading this file to test
the extension

00:00:09.500 --> 00:00:12.000
You can use this as a guide
for your own subtitle formats

00:00:12.500 --> 00:00:15.000
WebVTT files use the .vtt extension

00:00:15.500 --> 00:00:18.000
Timestamps are in format:
HH:MM:SS.MMM --> HH:MM:SS.MMM

00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:21.000
Subtitles can span multiple lines

00:00:21.500 --> 00:00:24.000
Just separate them with blank lines

00:00:24.500 --> 00:00:27.000
That's all you need to know!

00:00:27.500 --> 00:00:30.000
Have fun with Sub Loader 🎬
